Quick shortcuts
  • Tab - Add a subtopic to left side
  • Shift + Tab - Add a subtopic to right side
  • Enter - Add a sibling subtopic to top
  • Delete - Delete a topic
  • F2 - Edit a topic
  • Esc - End a text editing
  • Arrow(Up, Down, Left, Right) - Navigate between topics
  • F1 - Show/Hide Short cut Key
